<h2 class="main">Enclosure</h2>
<h3 class="sub">Proposal for Frontier Forts</h3>

<div class="docbody">
<div class="opener"> 
<table class="salutationBlock">
        <tr>
		<td class="salutationRight">[c.9 November 1756]</td>
	      </tr>
      </table>
</div>
<p>A Plan of the number of Forts, and strength necessary to each, extending entirely across our Frontiers, from South to north.</p>
